## 4. JSX Section Dividers

Divide significant logical blocks inside JSX with inline comment labels. Use em-dash style
for comments that label a region with a note:

```tsx
{/* Backdrop â€” click closes menu */}
<div id="menu-backdrop" ... />

{/* Sidebar panel */}
<aside id="app-menu-panel" ... >

  {/* Move speed */}
  <label ...> ... </label>

  {/* Sound */}
  <label ...> ... </label>

  {/* Developer dock toggle */}
  <button ...> ... </button>
```

Rules:
- Every top-level JSX section within a component body gets a divider comment.
- Subsections within a panel or form get shorter comments without em-dash.
- Never leave large blocks of JSX without at least one orienting comment.

